{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ekron-town-shipwheel-1.gif?t=1731947653\" />Explore the island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you awaken on the shores of an enigmatic tropical island, you find yourself alone amidst the remnants of a bygone civilization intertwined with the echoes of a complex past. The island appears abandoned, with signs of a recent upheaval disturbing its peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ekron-beach-lightning-1.gif?t=1731947653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Search for meaning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover letters left behind to piece together a narrative that drives you to understand what happened. Not all is as it appears to be on the surface, and your progression will illuminate the mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ekron-town-toucan-1.gif?t=1731947653\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Understand and observe</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through exploration, observation, and problem solving, players must unravel the island\u2019s secrets and discover the fate of its previous inhabitants... and themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ekron-beach-lantern-1.gif?t=1731947653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unravel the mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover what happened to the villagers and learn why they disappeared. Explore their villages and you will find more than just hospitality. Through exploration, observation, and problem solving, players must unravel the island\u2019s secrets and discover the fate of its previous inhabitants... and themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731947653","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/page.bg.jpg?t=1731947653","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/a8384a549fc8e301cfa495933cc99712fe0b47e9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731947653","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/a8384a549fc8e301cfa495933cc99712fe0b47e9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731947653","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ekron-town-shipwheel-1.gif?t=1731947653\" />Explore the island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you awaken on the shores of an enigmatic tropical island, you find yourself alone amidst the remnants of a bygone civilization intertwined with the echoes of a complex past. The island appears abandoned, with signs of a recent upheaval disturbing its peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252290/extras/ekron-beach-lightning-1.gif?t=1731947653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Search for meaning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover letters left behind to piece together a narrative that drives you to understand what happened. Not all is as it appears to be on the surface, and your progression will illuminate the mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass